38:36.200 --> 38:44.200
This is the way Uzbekistan, Kazakhstan, Estonia,

38:44.200 --> 38:49.200
or the method of planned promotion,

38:49.200 --> 38:55.200
where the development of national standards is carried out,

38:55.200 --> 39:02.200
which is based on international standards of financial accounting,

39:02.200 --> 39:07.200
borrowing significant parts of the principles

39:07.200 --> 39:13.200
and changing existing national standards,

39:13.200 --> 39:21.200
as well as transferring most of the principles of international standards to national standards.

39:21.200 --> 39:29.200
Russia chose the most rational way of applying international financial reports.

39:29.200 --> 39:34.200
This is their adaptation,

39:35.200 --> 39:43.200
